long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: PhisX is a Chrome extension designed to safeguard users from phishing attacks by detecting and malicious URLs in real-time. Using advanced machine learning model, PhisX analyzes URLs as you browse, ensuring you don't fall victim to cybercriminals' tactics. The extension seamlessly integrates into your browsing experience, providing instant status of the website's URL. Whether you're shopping, banking, or just surfing the web, PhisX gives you the confidence to navigate the internet safely.
